juniPppoeProfileAgent.name: juniPppoeProfileAgent

revisions.description: Added PADR Remote Circuit Id Capture support.
Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Added PADI flag and packet trace support.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniPppoeProfileAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniPppoeProfileAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the PPPoE Profile component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniPppoeProfileAgentV1.name: juniPppoeProfileAgentV1
juniPppoeProfileAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the PPPoE Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.
        This version of the PPPoE Profile component was supported in JUNOSe 3.0
        and 3.1 system releases.
juniPppoeProfileAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when the duplicate MAC address indicator and AC-NAME were added.

juniPppoeProfileAgentV2.name: juniPppoeProfileAgentV2
juniPppoeProfileAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the PPPoE Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.
        This version of the PPPoE Profile component was supported in JUNOSe 3.2
        and subsequent 3.x system releases.
juniPppoeProfileAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for PADI flag and packet trace.

juniPppoeProfileAgentV3.name: juniPppoeProfileAgentV3
juniPppoeProfileAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the PPPoE Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.
        This version of the PPPoE Profile component was supported in JUNOSe 4.0
        thru 5.0 system releases.
juniPppoeProfileAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when service name table support was added.

juniPppoeProfileAgentV4.name: juniPppoeProfileAgentV4
juniPppoeProfileAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the PPPoE component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the PPPoE component was supported in JUNOSe 5.1 through 7.0
        system releases.
juniPppoeProfileAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when PADR remote-circuit-id field was added.

juniPppoeProfileAgentV5.name: juniPppoeProfileAgentV5
juniPppoeProfileAgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the PPPoE Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.
        This version of the PPPoE Profile component is supported in JUNOSe 7.0
        and subsequent system releases.
juniPppoeProfileAgentV5.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in JUNOSe.

juniPppoeProfileAgentV6.name: juniPppoeProfileAgentV6
juniPppoeProfileAgentV6.productrelease:
Version 6 of the PPPoE Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.
        This version of the PPPoE Profile component is supported in JUNOSe 7.0.1
        and subsequent system releases.
juniPppoeProfileAgentV6.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPPoE Profile application in JUNOSe.
